caption.center: PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF MICHIGAN, Plaintiff-Appellee, v. VANISSHA LAKE

opinion.opinion_text:
SC: 125674, COA: 244219, Ingham CC: 01-077752-FH.
On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the January 22, 2004 judgment of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the question presented should be reviewed by this Court.
